{{Expand Korean|성희안|date=November 2013}}
'''Seong Huian'''([[korea]]n:성희안;成希顔, 1461–1513) was a [[Korea]]n [[Joseon Dynasty]] politician and [[Neo-Confucianism]] Philosopher served as Prime Minister or Chief State Councillor during the reign of [[King Jungjong]] in 1513 until his death . He was one of the coup leaders and maximum merits to become [[Jungjong]] a King .<ref>[http://100.naver.com/100.nhn?docid=92511 Seong Huian] {{ko}}</ref>
==Popular culture== * Portrayed by Lee Hwa-ryong in the 2017 [[KBS2]] TV series ''[[Queen for Seven Days]]''.
== See also == * [[Jungjong coup]] * [[Bak Wonjong]] * [[Yu Sunjeong]]
